== Page Layout ==
Hello, I wanted to begin a Discussion on this article, to debate on the page layout. The only available badge to achieve at a regular user level is "Supporter". I wanted to know if there should be separate categories for "Former Badges" and "Special Badges" given that Early Supporter is no longer achievable, and the VRChat Team Alumni badge isn't a badge to shoot for. I also wanted to try to see if we can debate a category for "Proposed Badges" or "Upcoming Badges" since the badge for users contributing to the Crowdin localization for VRChat is not yet public.
-[[Special:MyLanguage/User:DAG-XR|DAG-XR]] ([[Special:MyLanguage/User talk:DAG-XR|talk]]) 02:10, 17 July 2024 (UTC)

